<p>Hail ! Prosperity ! In the 5th year of (<hi rend="italic">the reign of</hi>) king <hi rend="bold">Pārthivēndravarman</hi>, (<hi rend="italic">the following</hi>) is the sale deed <ta>(vilai kaieḻuttu)</ta> of us (<hi rend="italic">the members</hi>) of the assembly of <hi rend="bold">Kalikēsari-chaturvēdimaṅgalam</hi>, a <hi rend="italic">dēvadāna</hi> in its (<hi rend="italic">own</hi>) subdivision (<hi rend="italic">kūṟu</hi>) in <hi rend="bold">Puḻar-kōṭṭam</hi>• • • • </p>

